1) we need to copy an existing profile from chrome so that we can use the google account and we dont have to sign in with 2fa
sh copy-chrome-prof.sh 
copies the Default profile in chrome, you can specificy a profile if you want for multiple instances
2) we need to open chrome in debug mode and with open port so that puppetter can connect to it
# can be separately called in run-chrome.sh
3) run speech-pup.ts for pup to connect to the port and start it
# 2 and 3 is combined in pipeline.sh 